@startuml MCP_Nebras_Sequence
skinparam ParticipantPadding 20
skinparam BoxPadding 10

actor "LLM / AI Agent\n(e.g., Claude)" as Agent
box "Nebras MCP Module" #LightCyan
participant "MCP Server" as MCP
end box

box "Agentive Platform" #LightGoldenRodYellow
participant "API Gateway" as Gateway
participant "Cognitive Orchestrator" as Cog
end box

== 1. Tool Discovery ==
Agent -> MCP : ListToolsRequest
MCP --> Agent : Returns Tools:\n- nebras_initiate_consent\n- nebras_execute_salary_batch\n- nebras_execute_car_lease

== 2. Consent Flow Execution ==
Agent -> MCP : CallTool(nebras_initiate_consent, {scope: DOMESTIC_PAYMENT})
MCP --> Agent : Returns UAE Pass URL & Consent ID

== 3. Payment Execution ==
Agent -> MCP : CallTool(nebras_execute_salary_batch, {amount: 250000})
note over MCP : MCP Maps to Open Finance JSON Intent
MCP -> Gateway : POST /domestic-payments\n(Encrypted payload)
Gateway -> Cog : Route to Temporal Workflow
Cog --> Gateway : Intent ID
Gateway --> MCP : Intent ID
MCP --> Agent : Returns Success + Intent ID

== 4. AI Context Awareness ==
note over Agent : AI now knows the batch was submitted\nand can continue its autonomous reasoning.

@enduml
